TXT Report includes:

Clean, readable text format
Timestamp of scan
Complete list of discovered endpoints
Detailed vulnerability findings
Easy to view in any text editor

PDF Report includes:

Professional formatting with colors
Summary table with key metrics
Organized sections for endpoints and vulnerabilities
Color-coded severity levels (High=Red, Medium=Yellow, Low=Green)
Disclaimer and best practices notes
Timestamp and target information

JSON Report includes:

Machine-readable format
Perfect for automation or further processing
All scan data in structured format

The PDF report will look professional and is great for documentation or sharing with team members. The TXT format is perfect for quick reviews and can be easily parsed by other tools.
